%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20Grand%20Tour%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BSEAL%20Team%2C%26quot%3B%20runs%20the%20drone%20cinematography%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cinedrones.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECineDrones%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmikefortin%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20profile%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortin%20told%20the%20BBC%20that%20his%20drone%20company%20operated%20almost%20every%20day%20before%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhollywood-studios-and-writers-reached-agreement-to-end-strike-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHollywood%20writers'%20strike%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20ran%20from%20May%20until%20September%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftv-shows-bounce-back-new-rules-bring-pain-hollywood-points-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eactors%20also%20went%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20strike%20from%20July%202023%20and%20productions%20ground%20to%20a%20halt%2C%20work%20dried%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20year%20since%20the%20strikes%20ended%2C%20Fortin%20said%20he%20has%20flown%20drones%20for%20only%2022%20days%20and%20worked%20as%20an%20actor%20for%20just%2010%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20money%20became%20tighter%2C%20Fortin%20was%20evicted%20from%20his%20home%20in%20Huntington%20Beach%2C%20where%20he%20lived%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20two%20children%2C%20before%20moving%20to%20an%20apartment%20in%20Las%20Vegas%20%E2%80%94%20which%20they%20are%20also%20about%20to%20be%20evicted%20from%2C%20per%20the%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20saving%20to%20buy%20a%20house%2C%20we%20had%20money%2C%20we%20had%20done%20things%20the%20right%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Fortin%20said.%20%26quot%3BTwo%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20didn't%20worry%20about%20going%20out%20to%20dinner%20with%20my%20wife%20and%20kids%20and%20spending%20200%20bucks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20I%20worry%20about%20going%20out%20and%20spending%20%245%20on%20a%20value%20meal%20at%20McDonald's%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20writers'%20strikes%20lasted%20for%20nearly%20150%20days%20and%20resulted%20in%20the%20Writers%20Guild%20of%20America%20securing%20minimum%20pay%20increases%20and%20improvements%20to%20residuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20industry%20as%20a%20whole%20has%20suffered%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.otis.edu%2Fabout%2Finitiatives%2Fdocuments%2Fotis-college-report-creative-economy-june-2024.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efewer%20shows%20being%20ordered%20and%20budget%20cuts%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20number%20of%20productions%20filmed%20in%20the%20US%20was%20down%2037%25%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202024%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20period%20in%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftv-shows-bounce-back-new-rules-bring-pain-hollywood-points-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20data%20by%20tracking%20company%20ProdPro%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20workers%20employed%20by%20California's%20creative%20economy%20fell%20by%2070%2C840%20in%202023%2C%20with%20film%2C%20TV%2C%20and%20sound%20sectors%20accounting%20for%2059%25%20of%20those%20lost%20jobs%2C%20according%20to%20an%20Otis%20College%20of%20Art%20and%20Design%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20industry%20moved%20into%202024%2C%20crewmembers%20say%20work%20remained%20scarce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20LA-based%20location%20manager%20who%20was%20out%20of%20work%20for%20seven%20and%20a%20half%20months%20during%20and%20after%20the%20strikes%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fbusiness%2Fbusiness-news%2Fcrew-production-slowdown-1235843877%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Hollywood%20Reporter%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March%20that%20there%20hadn't%20been%20%26quot%3Bany%20real%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20industry%20is%20not%20back.%20What's%20back%20is%20a%20few%20things%20that%20are%20doing%20pickups%20or%20needed%20to%20restart%20from%20things%20that%20were%20shut%20down%20before%20May%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20set%20decoration%20buyer%20added%20that%20they%20could%20%26quot%3Bcount%20on%20two%20hands%26quot%3B%20how%20many%20people%20they%20knew%20that%20were%20working%20at%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Duncan%20Crabtree-Ireland%2C%20the%20national%20executive%20director%20and%20chief%20negotiator%20with%20the%20Screen%20Actors%20Guild%20union%2C%20told%20the%20BBC%20that%20he%20was%20hopeful%20that%20production%20would%20pick%20back%20up%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Hollywood%20%26quot%3Balways%20thinks%20it's%20in%20crisis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20town%20that%20constantly%20faces%20technological%20innovation%20%E2%80%94%20all%20kinds%20of%20change%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20magic.%20Part%20of%20keeping%20content%20fresh%20is%20everyone%20having%20the%20idea%20that%20things%20don't%20always%20have%20to%20be%20the%20way%20they've%20been%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortin%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20acknowledged%20that%20%26quot%3Bthings%20are%20coming%20in%20little%20by%20little.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHollywood%20gave%20me%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it%20feels%20like%20the%20industry%20has%20turned%20its%20back%20on%20lots%20of%20people%2C%20not%20just%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Michael%20Fortin%20and%20CineDrones%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20BI's%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20regular%20working%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhollywood-cinematographer-mcdonalds-eviction-writers-actors-strike-production-budgets-2024-9%5C%22%3EBu