C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMorocco%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Gary%20He%2C%20a%20Brooklyn-based%20photojournalist%2C%20received%20an%20unexpected%20surprise%20with%20his%20regular%20McDonald's%20order.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20pack%20of%20dates%20paired%20with%20a%20chebakia%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Maghrebi%20sweet%20made%20using%20deep-fried%20dough%20that's%20shaped%20like%20a%20rose%20and%20drizzled%20with%20honey%20syrup%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tomato%20and%20legumes%20soup%20called%20harira%20soup%2C%20and%20a%20bottle%20of%20laban%20or%20salted%20buttermilk%2C%20all%20packed%20in%20a%20tiny%20box.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurious%20about%20the%20box%20and%20its%20significance%2C%20He%20turned%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-european-court-upholds-antitrust-fine-search-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20find%20out%20more%20...%20only%20to%20find%20there%20wasn't%20much%20information%20available%20online.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20began%20researching%20McDonald's%20specialties%20in%20other%20countries%2C%20there%20was%20very%20little%20information%2C%20and%20most%20of%20it%20was%20very%20scattered%2C%26quot%3B%20He%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20the%20idea%20to%20document%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20restaurant%20chains%20in%20the%20world%20came%20about%20for%20He%2C%20who%20recalled%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20an%20opportunity%20to%20play%20a%20journalist%20and%20documentarian%20while%20also%20tapping%20into%20that%20lifelong%20love%20of%20McDonald's%20and%20combining%20it%20into%20a%20single%20project.%26quot%3B%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EFive%20years%20later%2C%20the%20James%20Beard%20Award-winning%20photojournalist%20has%20traveled%20to%20over%2055%20countries%20across%20six%20continents%20and%20compiled%20a%20420-page%20book%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmcatlas.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMcAtlas%3A%20A%20Global%20Guide%20to%20t