3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kishor%20charged%20the%20longest-serving%20CM%20of%20Bihar%20with%20running%20his%20government%20through%20a%20handful%20of%20%26quot%3Bretired%20bureaucrats%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%202025%20Bihar%20assembly%20polls%20would%20be%20fought%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20'three%20S'%2C%20that%20is%20'%3Cem%3Esarab%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(liquor)%2C%20'survey'%20(land)%20and%20'smart%20meter'%20and%20asserted%20that%20these%20issues%20would%20prove%20to%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Bfinal%20nail%20in%20the%20coffin%20for%20the%20current%20regime%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Nitish%20Kumar%20government%20is%20being%20run%20by%20four%20retired%20bureaucrats.%20The%20CM%20is%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20these%20babus.%20Neither%20Kumar%20nor%20these%20bureaucrats%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20problems%20being%20faced%20by%20the%20people.%20Kumar%20has%20changed%20now.%20He%20has%20lost%20his%20morality%20and%20is%20only%20interested%20in%20securing%20the%20chief%20minister's%20chair%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kishor%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20'Jan%20Suraj'%20initiative%20will%20become%20a%20political%20party%20on%20October%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20form%20the%20government%20after%20the%202025%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Bihar%2C%20we%20will%20end%20the%20liquor%20ban%20within%20one%20hour%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20existing%20prohibition%20law%20in%20the%20state%20is%20fake%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20has%20been%20incurring%20a%20%26quot%3Bloss%20of%20nearly%20Rs%2020%2C000%20crore%20every%20year%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20the%20%26quot%3Bliquor%20mafia%20and%20officials%20continue%20to%20make%20money%20from%20illegal%20trade%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Kishor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jan%20Suraj%20chief%20said%20he%20would%20continue%20to%20speak%20against%20the%20policy%20and%20was%20not%20afraid%20of%20losing%20votes%20of%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20I%20get%20votes%20of%20women%20or%20not%2C%20I%20will%20continue%20speaking%20against%20the%20liquor%20ban%20since%20it%20is%20not%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20Bihar%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727610900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fi6pk9778_prashant-kishor_625x300_29_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-government-in-grip-of-retired-babus-prashant-kishor-6677028%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Political%20strategist-turned-activist%20Prashant%20Kishor%20on%20Sunday%20launched%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20state%20government%20was%20being%20%26quot%3Brun%20by%20four%20retired%20bureaucrats%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20CM%20was%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bgrip%20of%20these%20former%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-government-in-grip-of-retired-babus-prashant-kishor-6677028%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PT%20Usha%20Breaks%20Silence%20On%20Accusations%20Of%20Running%20IOA%20In%20'Autocratic'%20Manner%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAccused%20of%20running%20the%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association%20in%20an%20%26quot%3Bautocratic%26quot%3B%20manner%2C%20its%20president%20PT%20Usha%20on%20Sunday%20hit%20back%20at%20the%20revolting%20executive%20council%20members%2C%20saying%20they%20%26quot%3Bseem%20more%20focused%20on%20self-serving%20power%20play%20and%20monetary%20gain%26quot%3B%20than%20working%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20the%20country's%20sport.%20In%20an%20official%20press%20release%2C%20Usha%20also%20alleged%20that%20%26quot%3Bsome%20of%20these%20EC%20members%20have%20very%20questionable%20track%20records%2C%20including%20allegations%20of%20gender%20bias%20and%20even%20cases%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20filed%20against%20them%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIn%20my%2045-year-long%20career%20as%20a%20sportsperson%20representing%20India%20...%20I%20have%20never%20encountered%20individuals%20so%20indifferent%20to%20the%20aspirations%20of%20our%20athletes%20and%20our%20nation's%20sporting%20future%20...%20these%20individuals%20seem%20more%20focused%20on%20self-serving%20power%20play%20and%20monetary%20gain%20through%20their%20prolonged%20presence%20and%20control%20in%20sports%20administration%2C%26quot%3B%20Usha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurther%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20bring%20to%20light%20that%20some%20of%20these%20EC%20members%20have%20very%20questionable%20track%20records%2C%20including%20allegations%20of%20gender%20bias%20and%20even%20cases%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20filed%20against%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20track%20legend%20without%20specifying%20any%20particular%20case%20or%20giving%20specific%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%2012%20members%20of%20the%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association%20(IOA)%20Executive%20Council%20shot%20off%20a%20letter%20to%20senior%20International%20Olympic%20Committee%20(IOC)%20official%20Jerome%20Poivey%2C%20accusing%20Usha%20of%20running%20the%20organization%20in%20an%20%26quot%3Bautocratic%26quot%3B%20manner%20and%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bmy%20way%20or%20the%20highway%26quot%3B%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20sent%20the%20letter%20to%20Poivey%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Institutional%20Relations%20and%20Governance%20at%20the%20IOC%2C%20after%20Usha%20rejected%20their%20demand%20of%20removing%20Raghuram%20Iyer%20from%20the%20IOA%20CEO's%20post%20during%20a%20stormy%20executive%20council%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revolting%20EC%20members%20wrote%20to%20Poivey%20that%20Iyer's%20appointment%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20ratified%20and%20they%20will%20re-advertise%20for%20the%20position%20of%20the%20IOA%20CEO%2C%20%26quot%3Baiming%20to%20appoint%20a%20suitable%20candidate%20within%20the%20next%20two%20months%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20vice%20president%20Ajay%20H%20Patel%2C%20vice%20presidents%20Rajlaxmi%20Deo%20and%20Gagan%20Narang%2C%20Treasurer%20Sahdev%20Yadav%2C%20Joint%20Secretaries%20Alaknanda%20Ashok%20and%20Kalyan%20Chaubey%2C%20other%20Executive%20Council%20members%20Amitabh%20Sharma%2C%20Bhupender%20Singh%20Bajwa%2C%20Rohit%20Rajpal%2C%20Dola%20Banerjee%2C%20Harpal%20Singh%20and%20Yogeshwar%20Dutt%20had%20signed%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETerming%20the%20accusations%20made%20by%20the%2012%20EC%20members%20as%20%26quot%3Bmalicious%20and%20false%26quot%3B%2C%20Usha%20said%20they%20%26quot%3Bare%20only%20intended%20to%20malign%20my%20leadership%20and%20the%20efforts%20of%20those%20working%20diligently%20towards%20the%20betterment%20of%20Indian%20sports%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20most%20egregious%20claims%20made%20by%20these%20EC%20members%20is%20questioning%20Mr.%20Raghuram%20Iyer's%20appointment%20as%20IOA%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20clarify%20that%20his%20appointment%2C%20made%20in%20January%202024%2C%20was%20carried%20out%20in%20strict%20accordance%20with%20the%20IOA%20constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20Sunday's%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20malicious%20letter%20from%20the%2012%20members%20of%20the%20IOA%20EC%20is%20part%20of%20a%20much%20broader%20attempt%20to%20hinder%20the%20progress%20of%20Indian%20sports%20and%20undermine%20the%20positive%20developments%20that%20we%2C%20as%20a%20collective%2C%20have%20worked%20hard%20to%20achieve.%20These%20actions%20not%20only%20tarnish%20the%20image%20of%20Indian%20sports.%26quot%3B%20Usha%20also%20levelled%20charges%20against%20Yadav%20and%20the%20Finance%20Committee%20members%20for%20%26quot%3Bsurreptitiously%20writing%20off%20large%20sums%20of%20money%20owed%20to%20the%20IOA%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRecently%2C%20during%20the%20CAG%20audit%2C%20it%20has%20come%20to%20my%20attention%20that%20IOA%20Treasurer%20Mr.%20Sahdev%20Yadav%2C%20in%20connivance%20with%20the%20members%20of%20the%20IOA%20Finance%20Committee%20headed%20by%20Mr.%20Ajay%20Patel%20and%20comprising%20of%20Mrs.%20Rajlaxmi%20Singh%20Deo%2C%20Mr.%20BS%20Bajwa%2C%20Mr.%20Amitabh%20Sharma%2C%20Mr.%20Rohit%20Rajpal%2C%20Lt.%20Gen.%20Harpal%20Singh%20and%20Ms.%20Monal%20Choksi%20have%20surreptitiously%20written%20off%20large%20sums%20of%20monies%20owed%20to%20the%20IOA%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdditionally%2C%20a%20case%20of%20using%20the%20IOA's%20PAN%20card%20by%20the%20Ad%20hoc%20committee%20in%20charge%20of%20Volleyball%2C%20headed%20by%20Mr.%20Rohit%20Rajpal%20and%20its%20member%20Ms.%20Alaknanda%20Ashok%2C%20is%20also%20being%20investigated%20since%20it%20was%20done%20without%20the%20necessary%20approvals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20former%20Acting%20CEO%2C%20Mr.%20Kalyan%20Chaubey%20bypassed%20IOA%20General%20Assembly%20to%20grant%20affiliation%20to%20the%20Taekwondo%20Federation%20of%20India%2C%20which%20is%20not%20recognised%20either%20by%20its%20World%20or%20Asian%20Federation%2C%20thereby%20causing%20imminent%20harm%20to%20our%20hard-working%20Taekwondo%20athletes.%26quot%3B%20She%20said%20despite%20these%20serious%20accusations%2C%20the%20revolting%20EC%20members%20continue%20to%20hold%20positions%20within%20the%20IOA%20and%20other%20National%20Sports%20Federations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20September%2010%20letter%2C%20Usha%20had%20sought%20explanation%20from%20Yadav%20on%20the%20allegations%20of%20%26quot%3Bfiling%20and%20furnishing%20false%20information%20in%20the%20IOA%2C%20misappropriation%20and%20writing%20off%20public%20money%20belonging%20to%20the%20IOA%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20IWLF%20(Indian%20Weightlifting%20Federation)%26quot