%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdhFnAxR57cNtGiwNUd-6vLAYAc75grvly3C10-854vFP4arw%2Fviewform%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22summary_bullets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20Google%20form%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDear%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20wife%20is%20an%20aggressive%20minimalist.%20We%20no%20sooner%20buy%20something%20than%20she's%20decided%20we%20don't%20need%20it%20and%20throws%20it%20in%20the%20trash.%20This%20is%20not%20how%20I%20want%20to%20live%20my%20life%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20a%20cheap%20way%20to%20live.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShe%20says%20this%20is%20our%20way%20of%20not%20participating%20in%20consumerism%2C%20but%20because%20of%20her%20penchant%20for%20tossing%20and%20donating%2C%20we're%20always%20buying%20and%20replacing%20everything.%20I've%20tried%20talking%20to%20her%20about%20it%2C%20and%20she%20calls%20me%20a%20hoarder.%20What%20should%20I%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20Today%2C%20Gone%20Tomorrow%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDear%20Here%20Today%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20situation%20sounds%20really%20frustrating.%20As%20difficult%20as%20the%20financial%20aspect%20may%20be%2C%20I%20imagine%20knowing%20that%20you%20might%20lose%20any%20or%20all%20of%20your%20belongings%20at%20a%20moment's%20notice%20induces%20a%20special%20kind%20of%20anxiety.%20You%20likely%20even%20reach%20a%20point%20where%20you%20stop%20buying%20things%20for%20the%20pleasure%20of%20it.%20After%20all%2C%20once%20your%20wife%20gets%20her%20hands%20on%20it%2C%20you'll%20never%20see%20it%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20stated%20in%20your%20letter%20that%20you%20%26quot%3Bdon't%20want%20to%20live%20this%20way.%26quot%3B%20You%20and%20your%20wife%20have%20a%20value%20issue.%20I%20imagine%20your%20wife%20doesn't%20view%20it%20as%20a%20tragedy.%20In%20fact%2C%20consciously%20or%20unconsciously%2C%20it's%20likely%20her%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomething%20tells%20me%20if%20your%20wife%20came%20home%20one%20day%20to%20a%20house%20like%20mine%20%E2%80%93%20one%20bursting%20with%20comfy%20furniture%2C%20memory%20boxes%2C%20floor-to-ceiling%20bookshelves%20lined%20with%20great%20literature%2C%20a%20tool%20shed%20full%20of%20everything%20you%20could%20ever%20need%20for%20any%20project%2C%20and%20a%20Tupperware%20cabinet%20full%20of%20containers%20without%20lids%20and%20lids%20without%20containers%20%E2%80%93%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20live%20this%20way%26quot%3B%20would%20be%20the%20understatement%20of%20her%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20I%20love%20my%20life.%20Yours%20sounds%20a%20little%20bleak%20to%20me%2C%20and%20apparently%20it%20does%20to%20you%20too.%20Unfortunately%2C%20however%2C%20there's%20no%20reason%20why%20you%20deserve%20your%20preferred%20lifestyle%20more%20than%20she%20does.%20Mismatched%20values%20can%20be%20very%20difficult%20to%20navigate%20in%20a%20marriage.%20But%20that%20truth%20cuts%20both%20ways.%20If%20you%20can't%20live%20this%20way%2C%20then%20something%20has%20to%20change%2C%20and%20your%20wife%20must%20open%20her%20heart%20to%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20reach%20these%20impasses%20in%20marriage%2C%20the%20key%20is%20to%20keep%20digging%20through%20the%20mire%20of%20disagreement%20until%20you%20reach%20the%20bedrock%20of%20harmony.%20I%20call%20it%20the%20bedrock%20because%20there%20must%20be%20a%20shared%20value%20on%20which%20you%20and%20your%20wife%20built%20your%20relationship.%20Find%20it%2C%20and%20use%20it%20again%20to%20build%20something%20new%20%E2%80%94%20a%20life%20you%20both%20enjoy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recognize%20this%20won't%20be%20as%20easy%20as%20a%20pretty%20metaphor%20makes%20it%20sound%2C%20however%2C%20so%20I%20have%20a%20couple%20suggestions.%20You%20mention%20that%20your%20wife%20sees%20her%20minimalism%20as%20a%20finger%20in%20the%20face%20of%20consumerism%2C%20and%20she%20calls%20your%20preferences%20%26quot%3Bhoarding.%26quot%3B%20While%20you%20both%20have%20a%20different%20take%20on%20what%20it%20should%20look%20like%2C%20it%20seems%20you%20share%20a%20common%20belief%20that%20frivolous%20spending%20isn't%20the%20answer.%20Lean%20into%20this%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20of%20your%20points%20of%20view%20on%20consumerism%20make%20sense.%20Your%20wife%20is%20right%2C%20materialism%20tends%20to%20lead%20to%20spending%2C%20and%20if%20you%20loathe%20unnecessary%20stuff%2C%20chances%20are%20you%20won't%20be%20mindlessly%20accumulating%20it.%20But%20as%20you%20said%2C%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20good%20quality%20purchases%20that%20will%20save%20you%20from%20having%20to%20buy%20more%20things%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20if%20you%20two%20are%20coffee%20drinkers%2C%20a%20coffee%20grinder%2C%20French%20press%2C%20coffee%20maker%2C%20milk%20frother%2C%20and%20a%20few%20coffee%20mugs%20and%20travel%20thermos%20are%20all%20purchases%20that%20will%20save%20you%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20a%20year.%20However%2C%20they%20will%20also%20clutter%20your%20kitchen.%20Try%20to%20show%20your%20wife%20the%20financial%20trade-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20you%20didn't%20get%20into%20specifics%20in%20your%20letter%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20particular%20areas%20your%20wife's%20compulsive%20clearing%20out%20is%20costing%20you%2C%20but%20I%20suggest%20you%20begin%20taking%20inventory.%20Whether%20she%20is%20tossing%20valuable%20items%20simply%20because%20she%20doesn't%20recognize%20their%20function%20or%20she's%20failing%20to%20forecast%20the%20ways%20these%20objects%20will%20be%20used%20again%20later%2C%20make%20a%20list%20and%20do%20the%20math.%20Show%20her%20how%20her%20habit%20is%20affecting%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbudgeting%5C%22%3Ebudget%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20shared%20value%20you%20could%20tap%20into%20is%20your%20love%20as%20a%20couple.%20If%20she%20is%20throwing%20away%20or%20donating%20your%20personal%20belongings%2C%20that%20is%20unkind%2C%20and%20considering%20her%20motive%20is%20ultimately%20a%20personal%20preference%2C%20she's%20also%20being%20selfish.%20Not%20that%20you%20should%20accuse%20her%20of%20this%20%E2%80%94%20those%20kinds%20of%20charges%20are%20rarely%20helpful.%20But%20I%20do%20think%20you%20should%20be%20honest%20with%20her%20about%20how%20her%20behaviors%20make%20you%20feel.%20You%20love%20this%20woman%2C%20so%20I%20am%20sure%20she%20has%20a%20good%20heart%2C%20and%20she%20doesn't%20want%20to%20hurt%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20it's%20time%20you%20told%20her%20that%20you%20feel%20hurt%20by%20her%20actions.%20Use%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%26quot%3B%20language%20so%20she%20doesn't%20get%20defensive.%20Tell%20her%20something%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20sad%20when%20I'm%20excited%20about%20a%20new%20purchase%20and%20then%20find%20out%20it's%20been%20thrown%20in%20the%20trash.%26quot%3B%20You%20can%20also%20say%20that%20you%20don't%20want%20her%20to%20suffer%20in%20a%20cluttered%20home%20that%20makes%20her%20skin%20crawl%2C%20but%20that%20your%20experience%20of%20her%20minimalism%20has%20been%20a%20largely%20negative%20one.%20Neither%20of%20you%20are%20bad%20people%20for%20having%20preferences%2C%20but%20you%20have%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20live%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERooting%20for%20you%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELooking%20for%20advice%20on%20how%20your%20savings%2C%20debt%2C%20or%20another%20financial%20challenge%20is%20affecting%20your%20relationships%3F%20Write%20to%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%20using%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdhFnAxR57cNtGiwNUd-6vLAYAc75grvly3C10-854vFP4arw%2Fviewform%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F