%20up%20with%20two%20endings%3A%20one%20that%20was%20similar%20to%20Brown's%20book%20ending%20and%20teased%20a%20sequel%2C%20and%20another%20that%20wrapped%20up%20the%20whole%20story.%20He%20then%20presented%20both%20to%20the%20executives%20at%20DreamWorks%20Animation%2C%20the%20studio%20behind%20the%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20their%20credit%2C%20they%20unanimously%20said%2C%20'Do%20the%20other%20ending%2C%20do%20the%20one%20that's%20true%20to%20the%20book%2C'%26quot%3B%20Sanders%20recalled.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20tougher%20ending%20because%20you%20have%20got%20to%20stick%20the%20landing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20the%20full%20backing%20of%20the%20studio%2C%20Sanders%20went%20forth%20with%20the%20more%20open%20ending.%20The%20result%20is%20filled%20with%20emotion%20and%20the%20thrill%20of%20what's%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWarning%3A%20Spoilers%20ahead%20for%20%26quot%3BThe%20Wild%20Robot%26quot%3B%20book%20and%20movie.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a44dd667-6dc6-49e7-ac7c-68a6129a7ce1%5C%22%3E'The%20Wild%20Robot'%20movie's%20ending%20is%20more%20cinematic%20than%20the%20book's%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Roz%20the%20robot%20in%20front%20of%20a%20ship%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f69e60de59ade1a3b52e17%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22816%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Wild%20Robot.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EDreamWorks%20Animation%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Brown's%20book%2C%20three%20combat%20robots%20known%20as%20RECOS%20come%20to%20the%20island%20to%20take%20Roz%20back%20to%20their%20makers.%20After%20a%20battle%20between%20the%20robots%20and%20Roz%2C%20alongside%20the%20animals%20on%20the%20island%2C%20Roz%20is%20just%20a%20head%20and%20torso.%20She%20decides%20she%20must%20return%20to%20her%20makers%20to%20be%20repaired%20and%20keep%20them%20from%20returning