hief%20Minister.%20He%20is%20the%20third%20generation%20leader%20in%20his%20family%20to%20get%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20after%20his%20grandfather%20and%20DMK%20veteran%20late%20M%20Karunanidhi%20and%20his%20father%20MK%20Stalin.%20The%2046-year-old%20leader%20did%20not%20take%20oath%20at%20today's%20event%20because%20he%20was%20a%20minister%20before%20his%20elevation%20to%20the%20Number%202%20post%20in%20the%20state%20government.%20He%20was%20seen%20congratulating%20the%20four%20ministers%20after%20the%20oath%20ceremony%20at%20Raj%20Bhavan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20said%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post%20that%20'Deputy%20Chief%20Minister'%20is%20not%20a%20position%20but%20a%20responsibility%20for%20him.%20He%20also%20visited%20the%20memorials%20of%20his%20grandfather%20M%20Karunanidhi%20and%20social%20activist%20Periyar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUdhayanidhi%20Stalin's%20elevation%20to%20the%20top%20post%20has%20drawn%20sharp%20criticism%20from%20AIADMK%20and%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIADMK%20spokesperson%20Kovai%20Sathyan%20referred%20to%20junior%20Stalin%20as%20%26quot%3Bprince%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20his%20elevation%20marks%20the%20end%20of%20DMK%20before%20the%202026%20state%20polls.%20%26quot%3BThis%20exposes%20what%20a%20big%20liar%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20is.%20Before%20the%202021%20election%2C%20he%20said%20his%20son%2C%20son-in-law%2C%20or%20anyone%20from%20his%20family%20won't%20venture%20into%20politics.%20This%20signals%20what%20we%20have%20been%20saying.%20This%20is%20dynast%20rule%20in%20the%20name%20of%20democracy.%20DMK%20means%20only%20one%20family.%20This%20is%20a%20black%20day%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20too%2C%20has%20targeted%20the%20DMK%20and%20said%20the%20party's%20history%20has%20been%20marked%20with%20%26quot%3Byears%20of%20betrayal%20of%20the%20people%20and%20prioritising%20family%20interests%20over%20pub