0blue%20sweater%20and%20smiling%20at%20the%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f73d2fde59ade1a3b58aa9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222408%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMargery%20Berger%20realized%20she%20wasn't%20as%20close%20to%20her%20ex's%20family%20anymore%20after%20her%20ex-sister-in-law%20died.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Margery%20Berger%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20was%20close%20with%20my%20in-laws%20when%20my%20ex-husband%20and%20I%20were%20married.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20the%20divorce%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20keep%20those%20relationships%20the%20same.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20when%20my%20ex-sister-in-law%20Barbara%20died%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20things%20had%20changed%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20sister-in-law%20died%20five%20years%20after%20her%20brother%20and%20I%20divorced%2C%20but%20in%20my%20mind%2C%20I%20was%20still%20married%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20family.%20They%20were%20with%20me%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-mom-died-young-im-worried-i-will-too-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emy%20mother%20died%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20when%20both%20of%20our%20kids%2C%20now%20adults%2C%20were%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20met%20my%20ex-husband's%20sisters%20over%2030%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20gained%20not%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprise-engagement-at-wedding-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esisters-in-law%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20sisters-for-life.%20Barbara%2C%2010%20years%20older%20than%20me%2C%20had%20large%20dark%20eyes%20and%20wore%20big%20rings%20on%20her%20small%20fingers%2C%20but%20on%20her%2C%20they%20looked%20good.%20She%20knew%20about%20literature%2C%20art%2C%20and%20design%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20read%20everything%20she%20read.%20If%20you%20didn't%20know%20that%20she%20had%20studied%20at%20the%20Cordon%20Bleu%2C%20you%20could%20have%20guessed%20when%20you%20sat%20down%20at%20her%20dinner%20table.%20And%20my%20favorite%20thing%20about%20her%20was%20how%20easily%20and%20loudly%20she%20laughed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20me%20stories%20about%20my%20ex-husband%20during%20our%20frequent%20hourlong%20phone%20conversations.%20When%20I%20told%20her%20how%20beautiful%20one%20of%20his%20ex-girlfriends%20was%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20but%20you%20can%20see%20too%20much%20of%20her%20upper%20gums%20when%20she%20smiles.%26quot%3B%20I%20always%20felt%20like%20she%20was%20on%20my%20side.%20When%20Barbara%20heard%20my%20ex-husband%20and%20I%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-avoid-divorce-according-to-lawyer-marriage-tips-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20divorced%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20was%20angry%20at%20him.%20I%20loved%20her%20even%20more%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ab7133d-9ae4-4a56-9e93-2841a7dd7799%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20Barbara%20died%2C%20the%20family%20invited%20me%20to%20her%20house%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Barbara's%20death%20in%202013%2C%20my%20ex%2C%20his%20girlfriend%2C%20and%20other%20family%20members%20went%20through%20her%20house%20to%20see%20what%20they%20wanted%20to%20keep%20and%20what%20they%20wanted%20to%20send%20to%20auction.%20After%20everyone%20else%20labeled%20their%20selections%2C%20they%20sent%20me%20a%20list%20of%20what%20was%20left%20and%20invited%20me%20to%20the%20house%20in%20Maine%20to%20see%20if%20I%20wanted%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20I%20was%20the%20ex-sister-in-law%2C%20I%20had%20loved%20Barbara%20like%20a%20sister%2C%20and%20in%20my%20mind%2C%20that%20made%20me%20family.%20I%20was%20not%20surprised%20that%20I%20was%20given%20the%20opportunity%20to%20go%20through%20Barbara's%20things%2C%20because%20I%20had%20tried%20to%20remain%20part%20of%20the%20family%20after%20I%20got%20divorced%20five%20years%20earlier.%20I%20sent%20birthday%20presents%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-love-my-mother-in-law-more-than-my-husband-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emy%20mother-in-law%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sisters-in-law.%20I%20included%20them%20and%20my%20ex-husband%20and%20his%20girlfriend%20in%20holiday%20dinners%2C%20even%20though%20they%20no%20longer%20invited%20me%20to%20theirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20told%20myself%20I%20was%20doing%20it%20for%20my%20kids%20so%20that%20they%20could%20be%20with%20all%20of%20us%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20But%20now%20I%20realize%20I%20was%20doing%20it%20for%20me%2C%20to%20stay%20connected%20to%20family.%20My%20mother%20had%20died%20many%20years%20earlier%2C%20I%20never%20knew%20my%20father%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20have%20siblings%2C%20so%20to%20me%2C%20this%20family%20was%20everything.%20That's%20why%20it%20meant%20so%20much%20to%20me%20when%20they%20bought%20me%20a%20silver%20and%20gold%20chain%20link%20bracelet%2C%20the%20same%20one%20they%20wore.%20Best%20of%20all%2C%20they%20always%20introduced%20me%20to%20people%20as%20their%20sister%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20like%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20drove%20up%20to%20Barbara's%20house%20where%20we%20had%20spent%20many%20summers%20with%20our%20kids%2C%20the%20garden%20was%20in%20bloom%2C%20evidence%20of%20what%20I%20admired%20about%20Barbara's%20aesthetic%20%E2%80%94%20planned%2C%20but%20not%20overly%20manicured.%20From%20the%20front%20door%2C%20I%20saw%20the%20rocky%20coast%20of%20Maine%20and%20the%20Atlantic%20Ocean%20out%20back.%20The%20house%20held%20so%20many%20memories%2C%20but%20I%20no%20longer%20felt%20like%20I%20belonged%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20I%20was%20like%20any%20other%20guest%20oohing%20and%20aahing%20at%20the%20view.%20When%20I%20walked%20by%20the%20fireplace%2C%20I%20flashed%20back%20to%20the%20many%20evenings%20we%20made%20s'mores%20and%20me%20yelling%20at%20my%20son%20to%20keep%20the%20burning%20marshmallows%20by%20the%20fireplace%20and%20away%20from%20the%20furniture.%20When%20I%20en