20it%20was%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Margery%20Berger%20wearing%20a%20grey%20sweatshirt%20sitting%20on%20a%20couch.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f73d4dde59ade1a3b58aae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMargery%20Berger%20still%20wears%20her%20ex-sister-in-law's%20sweatshirt.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Margery%20Berger%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20things%20remind%20me%20of%20Barbara%20daily%2C%20it%20is%20the%20thing%20I%20took%20without%20telling%20anyone%20that%20means%20the%20most%20to%20me.%20During%20my%20night%20alone%20in%20her%20house%2C%20I%20was%20cold.%20I%20went%20into%20Barbara's%20closet%20and%20found%20a%20gray%20pullover%20fleece%20that%20flared%20out%20at%20the%20bottom.%20It%20was%20way%20too%20big%20for%20me%2C%20but%20when%20I%20pulled%20it%20over%20my%20head%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20wasn't%20going%20to%20give%20it%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wore%20it%20over%20my%20pajamas%20in%20her%20guest%20room%20and%20took%20it%20with%20me%20the%20next%20day.%20I%20imagined%20that%20Barbara%20would%20have%20been%20happy%20that%20I%20had%20something%20more%20personal%20than%20a%20sculpture%20or%20a%20soup%20ladle.%20She%20would%20understand%20that%20her%20sweatshirt%20would%20remind%20me%20of%20our%20cool%20summer%20nights%20in%20Maine%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsibling-relationships-can-be-complicated-and-change-through-the-years-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebond%20we%20had%20as%20sisters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2278e575cd-fc7c-4aec-8cd1-12aa883f7738%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20bond%20with%20the%20family%20is%20no%20longer%20as%20close%2C%20but%20I%20understand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20month%20later%2C%20I%20went%20back%20to%20the%20house%20for%20the%20memorial%20service%20held%20only%20for%20family%20and%