was%20no%20way%20he%20would%20accompany%20me%2C%20so%20I%20went%20with%20a%20student%20who%20was%20also%20connected%20with%20the%20fundraiser%20who%20made%20her%20appointment%20on%20the%20same%20day%20as%20me.%20No%20one%20else%20I%20knew%20would%20go%20with%20me%2C%20so%20this%20would%20otherwise%20have%20been%20a%20solo%20odyssey.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e7bd5bbe-df51-4e31-87a9-f4ac2ef1d587%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20day%20of%20the%20jump%20arrived%2C%20and%20I%20was%20excited%20but%20nervous%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20arrived%20at%20the%20West%20Point%20Skydiving%20facility%20near%20West%20Point%2C%20Maryland%2C%20in%20the%20early%20fall%20morning%20as%20instructed.%20We%20were%20scheduled%20on%20the%20last%20flight%20since%20we%20were%20the%20only%20tandem%20jumpers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20hours%2C%20we%20watched%20from%20the%20hangar%20on%20the%20ground%20as%20many%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworlds-oldest-skydiver-shares-his-longevity-secrets-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esolo%20jumpers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20went%20up%20in%20the%20propeller%20airplane%2C%20which%20had%20a%20large%20freight%20door%20that%20opened%20wide%20enough%20to%20make%20it%20easy%20to%20jump%20from.%20They%20were%20not%20part%20of%20the%20fundraiser%2C%20and%20several%20made%20multiple%20jumps%2C%20returning%20to%20the%20air%20hangar%20after%20each%20one%20to%20carefully%20refold%20their%20parachutes%2C%20a%20lifesaving%20yet%20mundane%20task.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20each%20successive%20take-off%2C%20my%20anxiety%20grew.%20I%20thought%20watching%20everyone%20else%20return%20safely%20would%20make%20me%20braver%2C%20but%20it%20only%20increased%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fwhat-is-anxiety%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emy%20anxiety%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFinally%2C%20it%20was%20our%20turn.%20We%20put%20on%20orange%20jumpsuits%20and%20small%20helmets%20with%20goggles.%20We%20were%20strapped%20to%20the%20front%20of%20the%20bodies%20of%20our%20tandem%20jump%20partners%2C%20experienced%20jumpers%20who%20would%20wear%20the%20parachutes%20and%20oversee%20our%20adventure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20boarded%20the%20plane%20and%20took%20off.%20While%20flying%2C%20we%20watched%20several%20solo%20jumpers%20leap%20from%20the%20plane.%20Watching%20them%20jump%20made%20me%20feel%20as%20if%20I%20had%20taken%20leave%20of%20my%20senses.%20The%20joke%20everyone%20passed%20around%20was%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20would%20anyone%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F104-year-old-skydiver-dorothy-hoffner-dies-world-record-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ejump%20out%20of%20a%20perfectly%20good%20airplane%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20watching%2C%20we%20received%20a%20quick%20overview%20of%20the%20experience.%20We%20were%20told%20we'd%20leave%20the%20plane%20backwards%20and%20bend%20our%20knees%20so%20our%20feet%20would%20clear%20the%20plane%20easily.%20We%20were%20also%20told%20to%20jump%20away%20from%20the%20plane%20to%20avoid%20the%20propellers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jackie%20Fishman%20jumping%20out%20of%20a%20plane%20in%20a%20tandem%20skydive.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f6dd1bde59ade1a3b55138%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221366%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJackie%20Fishman%20was%20nervous%20to%20try%20skydiving.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20West%20Point%20Skydiving%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c80bc048-cbf6-4a7a-ab03-709471a7c875%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EJumping%20out%20of%20a%20plane%20was%20like%20nothing%20else%20I'd%20ever%20done%20%E2%80%94%20or%20will%20do%20again%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20recommended%20height%20for%20a%20first-time%20tandem%20jump%20is%20at%20least%2010%2C000%20feet%20to%20give%20about%20a%20minute%20in%20free%20fall%2C%20where%20you%20are%20rushing%20toward%20Earth%20before%20you%20need%20to%20deploy%20the%20parachute.%20My%20jump%20was%20at%20around%2012%2C000%20feet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20left%20the%20plane%20and%20did%20a%20backward%20flip%2C%20and%20immediately%2C%20the%20force%20of%20the%20air%20caused%20my%20cheeks%20to%20flap%20and%20flatten%20against%20the%20sides%20of%20my%20face%20in%20the%20rushing%20wind.%20Was%20this%20because%20I%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F60-year-old-woman-reduced-biological-age-to-35-tricks-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E60%20years%20old%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20or%20is%20it%20something%20that%20happens%20to%20all%20jumpers%3F%20The%20feeling%20was%20odd%20and%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20a%20slack-faced%20hound%20dog.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20retained%20the%20sky%20diving%20company's%20photographer%20to%20take%20photos%2C%20and%20he%20jumped%20before%20us%20with%20his%20camera%20mounted%20on%20his%20helmet.%20He%20took%20pictures%20and%20video%20as%20we%20rocketed%20toward%20Earth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221821%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jackie%20Fishman%20gave%20a%20thumbs-up%20to%20the%20photographer%20while%20skydiving.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f6dd45f9f6733e4be05535%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221366%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJackie%20Fishman%20understands%20why%20people%20enjoy%20skydiving.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20West%20Point%20Skydiving%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20rushing%20air%20prevented%20me%20from%20looking%20down%20at%20the%20approaching%20ground.%20Instead%2C%20I%20looked%20at%20the%20photographer%20who%20was%20falling%20close%20to%20us.%20I%20made%20the%20thumbs-up%20sign%20with%20both%20hands%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20photos%20and%20then%20realized%20I%20couldn't%20change%20my%20gesture%20as%20my%20hands%20were%20frozen%20in%20place%20by%20fear.%20We%20continued%20to%20rush%20closer%20to%20earth%20until%20the%20time%20to%20pull%20the%20parachute.%20My%20tandem%20buddy%20offered%20to%20let%20me%20pull%20it%2C%20but%20I%20declined%20(what%20if%20I%20messed%20up%3F!).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20soon%20as%20the%20parachute%20deployed%2C%20we%20were%20yanked%20up.%20Then%20we%20gently%20floated%20like%20a%20newly%20fallen%20leaf%2C%20swaying%20and%20bobbing.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20marveled%20at%20the%20scenery%20and%20the%20elevation%20and%20finally%20enjoyed%20the%20ride.%20We%20looked%20out%20at%20Chesapeake%20Bay%20and%20the%20green%20trees%20and%20earth%20and%20small%20houses%20and%20fields.%20It%20was%20peaceful%20and%20I%20finally%20understood%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthrill-seeking-adventures-everyone-should-experience-2019-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20reason%20people%20jumped%20repeatedly%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%20made%20sense.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESticking%20the%20landing%20is%20important%2C%20and%20my%20tandem%20buddy%20gave%20me%20some%20pointers%20as%20we%20floated%20toward%20the%20ground.%20You%20want%20to%20land%20on%20the%20balls%20of%20your%20feet%2C%20bend%20your%20knees%20and%20do%20a%20little%20run.%20Our%20landing%20was%20perfect%20despite%20a%20stronger-than-desired%20wind.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShortly%20after%20we%20landed%2C%20I%20saw%20one%20of%20the%20solo%20jumpers%20land.%20They%20were%20swept%20up%20by%20the%20wind%20and%20landed%20on%20their%20head.%20Since%20it%20was%20a%20head%20injury%2C%20they%20were%20instructed%20not%20to%20move%20until%20an%20ambulance%20came%20to%20check%20them%2C%20but%20the%20paramedics%20determined%20they%20were%20OK.%20Seeing%20this%20situation%2C%20I%20realized%20how%20many%20natural%20and%20unpredictable%20forces%20can%20affect%20the%20success%20of%20a%20jump.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWould%20I%20do%20it%20again%3F%20I%20can%20safely%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20one%20and%20done.%26quot%3B%20But%20I'm%20glad%20I%20did%20it!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskydiving-experience-at-60-years-old-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727605681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f6daa7f9f6733e4be051ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskydiving-experience-at-60-years-old-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I've%20been%20interested%20in%20trying%20skydiving%20for%20decades%2C%20but%20finally%20decided%20to%20try%20it%20at%20the%20age%20of%2060.%20I%20get%20why%20people%20love%20it%20but%20won't%20go%20again.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jackie%20Fishman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskydiving-experience-at-60-years-old-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Would%20have%20given%20more%20than%20IMF%20if%20...'%3A%20What%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%20on%20aid%20to%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727605489000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113785861%2Cimgsize-758816.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fwould-have-given-more-money-than-imf-if-rajnath-singh-on-offering-financial-aid-to-pakistan%2Farticleshow%2F113785830.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20S