i.%20He%20also%20visited%20Periyar's%20memorial%20and%20the%20homes%20of%20his%20grandfather%20at%20Gopalapuram%20and%20CIT%20Colony%20in%20Chennai.%20In%20one%20of%20the%20photographs%2C%20his%20aunt%20and%20senior%20DMK%20leader%20K%20Kanimozhi%20is%20seen%20congratulating%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20slammed%20the%20DMK%20over%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin's%20elevation%20to%20the%20top%20post%20and%20said%20the%20party's%20history%20has%20been%20marked%20with%20%26quot%3Byears%20of%20betrayal%20of%20the%20people%20and%20prioritising%20family%20interests%20over%20public%20welfare%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BDespite%20being%20part%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%20DMK%20has%20denied%20its%20partners%20a%20share%20in%20power%20and%20instead%20appointed%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20as%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20BJP%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20alumnus%20of%20Loyola%20College%2C%20Chennai%2C%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20has%20worked%20in%20several%20movies%20as%20an%20actor%20and%20producer%20before%20an%20all-out%20foray%20into%20politics.%20He%20has%20led%20the%20DMK's%20student%20wing%20and%20was%20among%20the%20key%20faces%20of%20the%20party's%202021%20campaign%20for%20the%202021%20state%20polls%20in%20which%20it%20scored%20a%20thumping%20win.%20He%20was%20inducted%20as%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20MK%20Stalin%20government%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%20leader%20made%20national%20headlines%20last%20year%20when%20his%20remarks%20likening%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20to%20dengue%20and%20malaria%20sparked%20a%20massive%20row.%20Stressing%20that%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20is%20against%20the%20idea%20of%20social%20justice%2C%20he%20said%20at%20an%20event%2C%20%26quot%3BSanatana%20is%20like%20malaria%20and%20dengue%20and%20so%20it%20must%20be%20eradicated%20and%20not%20opposed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20claimed%20that%20the%20remark%20was%20a%20genocidal%20call%20and%20targeted%20Congress%20which%20was%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20DMK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20had%20said%20he%20never%20called%20for%20genocide.%20%26quot%3BSanatana%20Dharma%20is%20a%20principle%20that%20divides%20people%20in%20the%20name%20of%20caste%20and%20religion.%20Uprooting%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20is%20upholding%20humanity%20and%20human%20equality.%20I%20stand%20firmly%20by%20every%20word%20I%20have%20spoken.%20I%20spoke%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20oppressed%20and%20marginalized%2C%20who%20suffer%20due%20to%20the%20Sanatana%20Dharma.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727602020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Ffp1napl_udhayanidhi-stalin_625x300_29_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fudhayanidhi-stalin-tamil-nadu-not-position-but-responsibility-udhayanidhi-stalin-on-getting-top-post-6676283%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20not%20a%20position%2C%20but%20a%20responsibility%2C%20DMK%20leader%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20said%20today%2C%20hours%20after%20his%20father%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20announced%20his%20elevation%20to%20the%20top%20post.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fudhayanidhi-stalin-tamil-nadu-not-position-but-responsibility-udhayanidhi-stalin-on-getting-top-post-6676283%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Ash%20discussed%20KJo's%20support%20for%20Alia%20Bhatt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727601972000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113751856%2Cimgsize-73016.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fthrowback-when-aishwarya-rai-discussed-karan-johars-support-for-alia-bhatt-said-she-has-opportunities-literally-on-her-lap%2Farticleshow%2F113751839.cms%22%2C%22sum