ia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbreaking-boundaries-actresses-redefining-action-roles%2Farticleshow%2F113784354.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113784354.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBollywood's%20leading%20actresses%20are%20redefining%20action%20roles%20traditionally%20dominated%20by%20men.%20Stars%20like%20Katrina%20Kaif%2C%20Deepika%20Padukone%2C%20and%20Priyanka%20Chopra%20Jonas%20have%20taken%20on%20physically%20demanding%20roles%20involving%20high-stakes%20stunts%20and%20combat%20scenes.%20Their%20performances%20are%20reshaping%20female%20representation%20in%20Bollywood's%20action%20genre%2C%20setting%20a%20new%20precedent%20for%20future%20heroines.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbreaking-boundaries-actresses-redefining-action-roles%2Farticleshow%2F113784354.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Israel%20Killed%20Hezbollah%20Chief%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20In%20Beirut%20Bunker%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHezbollah's%20leader%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20was%20killed%20on%20Friday%20in%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%20targeting%20an%20underground%20bunker%20in%20Beirut.%20The%20meticulously%20planned%20attack%2C%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20Israeli%20Air%20Force%2C%20involved%20the%20collaboration%20of%20multiple%20intelligence%20agencies%20and%20resulted%20in%20the%20death%20of%20several%20senior%20Hezbollah%20officials%20alongside%20Nasrallah.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20took%20place%20in%20southern%20Beirut%20and%20targeted%20a%20heavily%20fortified%20bunker%20located%20over%2060%20feet%20underground.%20Nasrallah%20and%20other%20high-ranking%20members%20of%20the%20Iran-backed%20group%20had%20gathered%20to%20discuss%20strategies%20against%20Israel%2C%20amidst%20mounting%20pressure%20from%20Tehran%20to%20avoid%20immediate%20retaliatory%20actions%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fhow-israel-killed-hezbollahs-leader-in-underground-bunker-52946d6d%5C%22%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20is%20being%20described%20as%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20strikes%20on%20an%20urban%20centre%20in%20recent%20history%2C%20the%20Israeli%20military%20used%20nearly%2080%20tons%20of%20explosives%2C%20including%20approximately%2085%20specialised%20%E2%80%9Cbunker-buster%E2%80%9D%20bombs%20designed%20to%20penetrate%20deep%20into%20fortified%20structures.%20These%20munitions%2C%20capable%20of%20piercing%20through%20up%20to%2030%20metres%20of%20earth%20or%20six%20metres%20of%20reinforced%20concrete%2C%20were%20used%20to%20breach%20the%20bunker's%20defences%20and%20ensure%20the%20precision%20of%20the%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEverything%20we%20planned%20was%20executed%20precisely%2C%20with%20no%20errors%2C%20both%20in%20intelligence%2C%20the%20planning%2C%20with%20the%20planes%20and%20the%20operation%20itself.%20Everything%20went%20smooth%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20commander%20of%20the%20IAF's%2069th%20Squadron%20told%20reporters%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fisrael-knew-of-nasrallahs-location-for-months-some-ministers-opposed-hit-reports%2F%5C%22%3ETimes%20of%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bunker-buster%20bombs%20weigh%20between%20907%20kg%20and%201%2C814%20kg.%20The%20design%20of%20bombs%20traces%20back%20to%20advanced%20artillery%20developed%20during%20World%20War%20II%2C%20specifically%20the%20Rochling%20shells.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20campaign%20had%20intensified%2C%20with%20over%202%2C000%20airstrikes%20in%20Lebanon%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20attack.%20The%20attack%20also%20targeted%20Hezbollah's%20military%20assets%2C%20destroying%20crucial%20electronic%20equipment%20and%20a%20cache%20of%20missiles.%20Israeli%20military%20officials%20indicated%20that%20months%20of%20planning%20had%20gone%20into%20the%20operation%2C%20with%20real-time%20intelligence%20confirming%20Nasrallah's%20presence%20in%20the%20bunker%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20strike.%20Israeli%20spokesperson%20Nadav%20Shoshani%20told%20the%20WSJ%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20intelligence%20that%20Nasrallah%20was%20meeting%20with%20senior%20terrorists%2C%20and%20we%20acted%20accordingly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20authorised%20the%20strike%20while%20addressing%20the%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%20in%20New%20York.%20During%20his%20speech%2C%20Netanyahu%20condemned%20terrorism%20and%20stressed%20Israel's%20commitment%20to%20securing%20its%20borders.%20In%20his%20first%20public%20remarks%20following%20the%20attack%2C%20Netanyahu%20referred%20to%20Nasrallah%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20terrorist%2C%E2%80%9D%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CHis%20removal%20is%20essential%20to%20achieving%20our%20goals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideos%2Fembed-player%2F%3Fid%3D843260%26mute%3D1%26autostart%3D1%26mutestart%3Dtrue%26pWidth%3D100%26pHeight%3D100%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%20has%20already%20displaced%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20Israel-Lebanon%20border.%20The%20United%20Nations%20reported%20that%20over%202%2C00%2C000%20Lebanese%20civilians%20have%20been%20displaced%20in%20the%20last%20week%20alone%2C%20with%20many%20more%20expected%20to%20flee%20as%20the%20fighting%20intensifies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20vowed%20to%20continue%20its%20military%20operations%20against%20Hezbollah%20until%20the%20group%20ceases%20its%20attacks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727600820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fqjdd0ruo_hassan-nasrallah_625x300_29_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-israel-killed-hezbollah-chief-hassan-nasrallah-in-beirut-bunker-6676060%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hezbollah's%20leader%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20was%20killed%20on%20Saturday%20in%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%20targeting%20an%20underground%20bunker%20in%20Beirut.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-israel-killed-hezbollah-chief-hassan-nasrallah-in-beirut-bunker-6676060%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mumbai%20Indians%20Urged%20To%20Retain%20These%203%20Stars%2C%20Snub%20Captain%20Hardik%20Pandya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%20auction%20guidelines%20are%20out%2C%20with%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20opening%20the%20gate%20for%20franchises%20to%20retain%20a%20maximum%20of%206%20players%20each.%20While%20the%2010%20franchises%20would%20take%20a%20few%20days%20to%20chart%20out%20their%20plans%2C%20auction%20strategies%20and%20decide%20which%20players%20they%20wish%20to%20retain%2C%20fans%20and%20former%20cricketers%20have%20started%20to%20share%20their%20inputs%20on%20the%20matter.%20Former%20India%20cricketer%20Ajay%20Jadeja%20feels%20Mumbai%20Indians%20shouldn't%20retain%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Rather%2C%20should%20try%20to%20get%20him%20using%20RTM%20in%20the%20auction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Jadeja%2C%20who%20has%20also%20coached%20the%20Afghani