t%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20before%20Hezbollah%20leader%20Sayyed%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20was%20killed%20in%20an%20airstrike%20in%20Lebanon's%20Beirut%2C%20an%20Iranian%20mole%20informed%20Israeli%20authorities%20of%20his%20location%2C%20French%20newspaper%20Le%20Parisien%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20a%20security%20source%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20the%20report%20said%20the%20mole%20had%20informed%20Israeli%20authorities%20that%20Nasrallah%20would%20be%20at%20Hezbollah's%20underground%20headquarters%20in%20Beirut's%20southern%20suburbs%20to%20attend%20a%20meeting%20with%20several%20top%20members%20of%20the%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%201.30%20pm%20IST%20yesterday%20(11%20am%20Lebanon%20time)%2C%20Israel%20Defence%20Forces%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BHassan%20Nasrallah%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20able%20to%20terrorize%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%20Later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Hezbollah%20confirmed%20the%20news.%20%26quot%3BSayyed%20Hassan%20Nasrallah...%20has%20joined%20his%20great%2C%20immortal%20martyr%20comrades%20whom%20he%20led%20for%20about%2030%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Israel%20Boosted%20Spies%20In%20Fight%20Against%20Hezbollah%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20The%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20Israel's%20recent%20successes%20against%20Hezbollah%20are%20a%20direct%20result%20of%20the%20country's%20decision%20to%20devote%20far%20more%20intelligence%20resources%20to%20target%20Hezbollah%20after%20the%202006%20war%20with%20the%20Iran-backed%20group.%20The%20Israeli%20army%20and%20the%20intelligence%20agencies%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20failed%20to%20score%20a%20decisive%20victory%20in%20that%2034-day%20conflict.%20The%20war%20ended%20with%20a%20UN-brokered%20cease-fire%20and%20allowed%20Hezbollah%2C%20despite%20losses%2C%20to%20regroup%20and%20prepare%20for%20the%20next%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20that%20followed%2C%20Israel%20deployed%20a%20lot%20of%20resources%20to%20collect%20information%20about%20Hezbollah's%20leadership%20and%20strategy.%20Unit%208200%2C%20Israel's%20signals%20intelligence%20agency%2C%20built%20cutting-edge%20cyber%20tools%20to%20better%20intercept%20Hezbollah's%20cellphones%20and%20other%20communications%2C%20the%20NYT%20report%20said.%20New%20teams%20were%20created%20within%20combat%20ranks%20to%20ensure%20that%20valuable%20information%20was%20quickly%20passed%20on%20to%20soldiers%20and%20the%20air%20force%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Pager%20Bombs%20And%20Nasrallah's%20Admission%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20televised%20speech%2C%20Nasrallah%20had%20said%20Hezbollah%20suffered%20an%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented%20blow%26quot%3B%20after%20Israel%20detonated%20explosive-laden%20pagers%20and%20hand-held%20radios.%20The%20attacks%20killed%2037%20people%20and%20wounded%20nearly%203%2C000%20people%20in%20two%20days.%20Nasrallah%20had%20then%20warned%20Israel%20of%20%26quot%3Btough%20retribution%20and%20just%20punishment%2C%20where%20it%20expects%20it%20and%20where%20it%20does%20not%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Lebanese%20investigation%20found%20that%20the%20pagers%20had%20been%20booby-trapped%2C%20AFP%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20members%20had%20started%20communicating%20via%20pagers%20and%20walkie-talkies%20after%20Israel%20penetrated%20cellphones.%20But%20that%20did%20not%20protect%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mossad%2C%20the%20NYT%20report%20said%2C%20appears%20to%20have%20created%20a%20shell%20company%20in%20Budapest%20and%20made%20the%20pagers%20under%20license%20from%20a%20company%20in%20Taiwan.%20Before%20the%20pagers%20arrived%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20Israeli%20operatives%20installed%20explosives%20inside%20them.%20The%20operation%20was%20scaled%20to%20produce%20thousands%20of%20pagers%2C%20requiring%20sophisticated%20manufacturing%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETop%20Hezbollah%20Leaders%20Targeted%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20NYT%20report%2C%20Israel's%20investment%20in%20greater%20intelligence%20gathering%20first%20paid%20off%20in%202008%20when%20Mossad%20worked%20with%20the%20CIA%20to%20kill%20top%20Hezbollah%20operative%2C%20Imad%20Mugniyah%2C%20in%20Syria.%20In%202020%2C%20Qassim%20Suleimani%2C%20who%20headed%20Iran's%20Quds%20Force%2C%20flew%20to%20Syria's%20Damascus%20and%20drove%20in%20a%20convoy%20to%20Beirut%20to%20meet%20Nasrallah.%20Israel%20did%20not%20try%20to%20kill%20Nasrallah%20then%20for%20fear%20of%20starting%20a%20war.%20It%20passed%20on%20the%20information%20to%20the%20US%20and%20Suleimani%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20drone%20strike%20at%20Baghdad%20airport%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20October%207%20attacks%20by%20Hamas%20on%20Israeli%20cities%20set%20off%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%20As%20Israel's%20counterstrike%20set%20off%20a%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Hezbollah%20started%20targeting%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20Tel%20Aviv%20went%20all-out%20against%20Hezbollah.%20A%20strike%20on%20July%2030%20killed%20Fuad%20Shukr%2C%20one%20of%20the%20group's%20top%20military%20commanders.%20About%20three%20weeks%20later%2C%20a%20strike%20killed%20Ibrahim%20Aqil%2C%20head%20of%20Hezbollah's%20elite%20Radwan%20Force%2C%20and%2015%20other%20commanders.%20Days%20later%2C%20another%20strike%20killed%20Ibrahim%20Mohammed%20Kobeissi%2C%20who%20commanded%20several%20Hezbollah%20units%2C%20including%20a%20guided%20missiles%20unit.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20Mohammed%20Srur%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Hezbollah's%20drone%20unit%2C%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChip%20Usher%2C%20a%20former%20CIA%20analyst%20who%20has%20worked%20with%20Israeli%20intelligence%2C%20has%20told%20NYT%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20secrets%20of%20their%20success%20come%20down%20to%20a%20couple%20of%20factors.%20They%20have%20a%20fairly%20defined%20target%20deck.%20That%20makes%20it%20easier%20for%20them%20to%20bring%20a%20tremendous%20amount%20of%20focus%20to%20what%20they%20do.%20They're%20in%20a%20shadow%20war%20with%20Hezbollah%20and%20Iran.%20And%20they're%20extraordinarily%20patient.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727597640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fm6n38q2o_nasrallah_625x300_29_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhassan-nasrallah-hezbollah-iran-spy-told-israel-hezbollah-chiefs-location-before-airstrike-report-6675770%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hours%20before%20Hezbollah%20leader%20Sayyed%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20was%20killed%20in%20an%20airstrike%20in%20Lebanon's%20Beirut%2C%20an%20Iranian%20mole%20informed%20Israeli%20authorities%20of%20his%20location%2C%20French%20newspaper%20Le%20Parisien%20has%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhassan-nasrallah-hezbollah-iran-spy-told-israel-hezbollah-chiefs-location-before-airstrike-report-6675770%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bobby%20says%20he%20had%20a%20tough%20time%20breaking%20the%20image%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727597483000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113783279%2Cimgsize-30214.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbobby-deol-says-he-had-a-tough-time-breaking-the-image-says-i-wanted-to-do-something-out-of-my-comfort-zone-i-still-decided-to-go-for-it%2Farticleshow%2F113783290.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113783290.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBobby%20Deol%E2%80%99s%20willingness%20to%20embrace%20challenging%20roles%20reflects%20his%20growth%20as%20an%20actor.%20Initially%20apprehensive%20about%20playing%20a%20mute%20character%2C%20he%20ultimately%20found%20strength%20in%20stepping%20outside%20his%20comfort%20zone.%20He%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20out%20of%20my%20comfort%20zone...%20I%20still%20decided%20to%20go%20for%20it.%E2%80%9D%20This%20decision%20not%20only%20showcased%20his%20versatility%20but%20also%20resonated%20with%20audiences%20who%20appreciated%20the%20depth%20of%20his%20character.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbobby-deol-says-he-had-a-tough-time-breaking-the-image-says-i-wanted-to-do-something-out-of-my-comfort-zone-i-still-decided-to-go-for-it%2Farticleshow%2F113783290.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMost%20Difficult%20Decision%26quot%3B%3A%20Thai%20Farmer%20Forced%20To%20Kill%20Over%20100%20Crocodiles%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20farmer%20in%20northern%20Thailand%20was%20forced%20to%20cull%20more%20than%20100%20crocodiles%20from%20his%20farm%20as%20heavy%20floods%20raised%20fears%20that%20they%20could%20escape%20and%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20human%20lives.%20Natthapak%20Khumkad%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20a%20crocodile%20farm%20in%20Lamphun%2C%20explained%20that%20days%20of%20relentless%20rain%20had%20severely%20damaged%20the%20enclosures%20holding%20his%20Siamese%20crocodiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20animals%20at%20risk%20of%20escaping%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20kill%20125%20crocodiles%2C%20which%20measured%20up%20to%20three%20meters%20long.%20Mr%20Khumkad%20was%20particularly%20concerned%20that%20the%20reptiles%20might%20roam%20the%20flooded%20countryside%2C%20potentially%20attacking%20locals%20and%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%2C%20reported%20by%20CNN%20on%20Friday%2C%20took%20place%20in%20the%20Lamphun%20province%20following%20devastating%20monsoon%20rains%20that%20have%20swept%20across%20the%20region.%20In%20September%2C%20northern%20Thailand%20was%20hit%20by%20intense%20monsoon%20rains%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20landslides%20and%20floods%20that%20killed%20over%2020%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20make%20the%20most%20difficult%20decision%20of%20my%20life%20to%20kill%20them%20all.%20My%20family%20and%20I%20discussed%20if%20the%20wall%20collapsed%20the%20damage%20to%20people's%20lives%20would%20be%20far%20bigger%20than%20we%20can%20control.%20It%20would%20involve%20people's%20lives%20and%20public%20safety%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20farmer%20told%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Facebook%20post%2C%20Natthapak%20Khumkad%20showed%20the%20eroded%20walls%20of%20the%20crocodile%20pond%20and%20explained%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20the%20primary%20reason%20that%20forced%20me%20to%20make%20an%20urgent%20decision.%20On%20that%20day%2C%20it%20rained%20heavily%20non-stop.%20The%20underwater%20wall%20collapsed%2C%20which%20was%20very%20close%20to%20reaching%20the%20outer%20wall.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20clarified%20that%20although%20his%20staff%20attempted%20to%20block%20off%20the%20area%20to%20fix%20the%20pond%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%20the%20unceasing%20rain%20made%20the%20situation%20dangerous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20crisis%20that%20required%20an%20extremely%20urgent%20decision.%20I%20had%20to%20use%20the%20last%20resort%2C%20which%20was%20to%20remove%20the%20crocodiles%20from%20the%20farm%20by%20slaughtering%20them.%20If%20it%20wasn't%20absolutely%20necessary%2C%20we%20wouldn't%20have%20used%20this%20method.%20It%20was%20the%20best%2C%20fastest%2C%20and%20safest%20method%20in%20that%20situation%2C%20with%20the%20rain%20still%20pouring%20incessantly.%20Thank%20you%20for%20all%20the%20encouragement%20and%20understanding.%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0Natthapak%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publis