t%20injected%20into%20you.%20It's%20the%20same%20immune%20response%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20as%20per%20the%20NY%20Post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FDulLO6C0Dik%3Fsi%3DPED24gIrguT2TC58%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20during%20multiple%20lawsuits%20against%20COVID%20mandates%2C%20Mr%20Varma%20provided%20contradictory%20testimony%2C%20in%20which%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20COVID-19%20vaccine%20has%20been%20shown%20to%20offer%20those%20persons%20with%20a%20prior%20COVID-19%20infection%20greater%20protection%20against%20reinfection.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20arose%20after%20the%20footage%2C%20filmed%20by%20a%20hidden%20camera%20and%20released%20by%20podcaster%20Steven%20Crowder%2C%20showed%20Mr%20Varma%20discussing%20the%20limitations%20of%20vaccine%20mandates.%20Critics%20have%20since%20accused%20him%20of%20providing%20false%20testimony%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20growing%20call%20for%20legal%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECouncilwoman%20Joann%20Ariola%20(R-Queens)%20has%20accused%20Mr%20Varma%20of%20perjury%2C%20or%2C%20lying%20under%20oath%2C%20and%20emphasised%20that%20his%20misleading%20testimony%20led%20to%20vaccination%20mandates%20that%20harmed%20many%20New%20Yorkers.%20Ms%20Ariola%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CDr.%20Varma%20swore%20under%20oath%20that%20the%20vaccine%20was%20the%20most%20effective%20way%20to%20prevent%20the%20spread%20of%20new%20COVID%20strains%2C%20but%20in%20captured%20footage%2C%20he%20privately%20acknowledges%20that%20there%20was%2C%20in%20reality%2C%20no%20difference%20between%20vaccinations%20and%20natural%20immunity%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ariola%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20outright%20perjury%20.%20.%20.%20perjury%20that%20cost%20thousands%20their%20l