n%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20big%20and%20strong%20it%20is%2C%20and%20I%20tell%20you%20with%20all%20reassurance%2C%20confidence%20and%20reliance%20on%20God%20that%20this%20big%2C%20strong%20and%20unprecedented%20bow%20did%20not%20knock%20us%20down%20and%20will%20not%20knock%20us%20down%2C%20God%20willing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nasrallah%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENasrallah's%20rhetoric%20was%20aimed%20not%20only%20at%20Israel%20but%20also%20in%20support%20of%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20say%20to%20the%20enemy's%20government%2C%20army%20and%20society%2C%20that%20the%20Lebanese%20front%20will%20not%20stop%20before%20the%20aggression%20on%20Gaza%20stops%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20saying%20this%20for%2011%20months.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideos%2Fembed-player%2F%3Fid%3D843197%26mute%3D1%26autostart%3D1%26mutestart%3Dtrue%26pWidth%3D100%26pHeight%3D100%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESayyed%20Hassan%20Nasrallah's%20speech%20came%20amid%20escalating%20violence%20along%20the%20Israel-Lebanon%20border%2C%20where%20Israeli%20and%20Hezbollah%20forces%20have%20been%20clashing%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20September%2020%2C%20Israel%20carried%20out%20a%20targeted%20strike%2C%20killing%20Ibrahim%20Aqil%2C%20the%20commander%20of%20Hezbollah's%20elite%20Radwan%20unit%2C%20along%20with%2012%20others%20in%20Beirut.%20Aqil%20had%20been%20a%20senior%20figure%20in%20the%20organisation%20and%20was%20also%20wanted%20by%20the%20US%20for%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%201983%20bombing%20of%20the%20American%20embassy%20in%20Beirut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20described%20the%20operation%20as%20part%20of%20its%20broader%20efforts%20to%20weaken%20Hezbollah.%20As%20both%20sides%20escalated%20their%20attacks%2C%20fears%20of%20a%20broader%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hezbollah%20intensified%2C%20leaving%20civilians%20on%20both%20sides%20caught%20in%20the%20crossfire.%20Residents%20of%20border%20towns%20in%20southern%20Lebanon%20recounted%20that%20the%20bombardments%20were%20the%20most%20intense%20they%20had%20witnessed%20since%20hostilities%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternational%20mediators%2C%20including%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%2C%20have%20called%20for%20restraint%20to%20prevent%20the%20conflict%20from%20spiralling%20into%20a%20full-blown%20regional%20war.%20However%2C%20Nasrallah's%20last%20speech%20made%20clear%20that%20Hezbollah%20would%20not%20back%20down%2C%20with%20the%20leader's%20words%20echoing%20even%20after%20his%20death%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhatever%20the%20sacrifices%2C%20whatever%20the%20consequences%2C%20the%20resistance%20in%20Lebanon%20will%20not%20stop%20supporting%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%20who%20are%20oppressed%20in%20that%20holy%20land.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20airstrikes%20on%20Lebanon%20have%20killed%20over%201%2C000%20people%20and%20displaced%20nearly%20half%20a%20million%20since%20Monday.%20Meanwhile%2C%20in%20Gaza%2C%20the%20death%20count%20has%20now%20risen%20to%20nearly%2042%2C000%2C%20with%20almost%20the%20entire%20population%20of%20the%20region%20displaced%20due%20to%20relentless%20bombardment.%20The%20humanitarian%20crisis%20has%20deepened%2C%20with%20food%2C%20water%20and%20medical%20supplies%20dwindling%20under%20the%20continuous%20siege.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727590560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fg2jf79co_hassan-nasrallah_625x300_29_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhezbollah-chief-death-what-hezbollah-chief-said-in-his-last-speech-before-fatal-israeli-strike-6675027%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20what%20would%20become%20his%20final%20speech%20on%20September%2019%