3Cp%3EThose%20with%20partial%20hearing%20loss%20may%20be%20able%20to%20enjoy%20music%20that%20is%20played%20at%20a%20particular%20pitch%20or%20decibel%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESign%20language%20interpretation%20helps%20sign%20language%20users%20understand%20the%20lyrics%20of%20songs.%20Sign%20language%20interpreters%20have%20become%20more%20common%20at%20several%20large%20concerts%20with%20Lollapalooza%20being%20the%20first%20to%20do%20so%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeaf%20people%20also%20benefit%20from%20live%20captioning%20and%20lyrics%20provided%20in%20song%20streaming%20platforms%20like%20Apple%20Music%20and%20Spotify.%20Apple%20Music%20also%20has%20a%20playlist%20curated%20by%20Deaf%20people.%20You%20can%20learn%20more%20about%20how%20Persons%20with%20Hearing%20Impairment%20experience%20music%20using%20this%20link.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20leads%20one%20to%20ask%20a%20deeper%20question%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20can%20having%20accessible%20cultural%20events%20come%20to%20be%20the%20norm%20rather%20than%20the%20exception%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20simple%20answer%20to%20that%20is%20by%20generating%20awareness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20participating%20in%20several%20festivals%20this%20year%20that%20will%20attract%20diverse%20audiences%2C%20and%20we%20hope%20to%20have%20sign%20language%20interpreters%20present.%20The%20number%20of%20people%20who%20understand%20sign%20language%20isn%E2%80%99t%20what%20matters%3B%20rather%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334578%2Fcoda-child-of-deaf-adult-indian-sign-language-isl%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehaving%20sign%20language%20available%20helps%20raise%20awareness%20about%20its%20importance%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20simple%20presence%20can%20help%20everyone%20recognise%20and%20appreciate%20the%20Deaf%20community%2C%20which%20is%20a%20significant%20step%20toward%20greater%20understanding%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jishnu%20when%20asked%20about%20what%20Swarathma%20plans%20for%20future%20concerts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20glass-half-full%20perspective%2C%20sign%20language%20interpreters%20were%20rare%20in%20universities%2C%20workplaces%2C%20and%20courts%20just%20a%20decade%20ago.%20Today%2C%20however%2C%20they%20are%20increasingly%20becoming%20a%20common%20feature%20in%20these%20settings.%20With%20this%20positive%20shift%2C%20there%20is%20hope%20that%20such%20inclusivity%20will%20soon%20extend%20to%20cultural%20events%20as%20well%2C%20making%20them%20more%20accessible%20to%20the%20Deaf%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20efforts%20are%20not%20merely%20about%20fulfilling%20legal%20mandates%20or%20ticking%20boxes%20%E2%80%94%20they%20represent%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20that%20culture%2C%20music%2C%20and%20social%20gatherings%20are%20integral%20to%20the%20human%20experience%2C%20and%20should%20be%20available%20to%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20an%20interpreter%2C%20I%20am%20only%20invited%20to%20certain%20types%20of%20events%20%E2%80%94%20seminars%2C%20conferences%2C%20or%20corporate%20workshops.%20Hardly%20do%20we%20ever%20come%20across%20an%20invite%20to%20interpret%20a%20play%20or%20a%20concert.%20This%20needs%20to%20change.%20By%20not%20including%20the%20community%20at%20cultural%20events%20or%20gatherings%2C%20they%20continue%20to%20stay%20in%20their%20bubbles%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Annu%20Malik%2C%20who%20is%20an%20ISL%20interpreter%20and%20special%20educator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20each%20event%20that%20embraces%20inclusivity%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20through%20interpreters%2C%20captioning%2C%20or%20other%20innovations%20%E2%80%94%20we%20move%20one%20step%20closer%20to%20a%20world%20where%20the%20Deaf%20community%20can%20fully%20engage%20in%20cultural%20life.%20Over%20time%2C%20what%20is%20seen%20as%20innovative%20today%20will%2C%20hopefully%2C%20become%20standard%20practice%20across%20cultural%20landscapes%2C%20ensuring%20equal%20participation%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWritten%20by%20v-shesh%3B%20Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fen%2Fobservances%2Fsign-languages-day%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EUnited%20Nations%20International%20Day%20of%20Sign%20Languages%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fec.europa.eu%2Feurostat%2Fweb%2Fquality-of-life%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEurostat%20Quality%20of%20Life%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fec.europa.eu%2Feurostat%2Fstatistics-explained%2Findex.php%3Ftitle%3DQuality_of_life_indicators_-_social_interactions%23%3A~%3Atext%3DKey%2520points%2520on%2520social%2520interactions%2C-Frequent%2520and%2520rewarding%26text%3DAside%2520from%2520encompassing%2520our%2520basic%2Cinterpersonal%2520trust%2520and%2520social%2520cohesion%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEurostat%20Quality%20of%20life%20indicators%20%E2%80%93%20social%20interactions%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Fbuzz%2Fthis-sign-language-interpreter-rocking-out-at-lollapalooza-mumbai-is-a-whole-vibe-6967975.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThis%20Sign%20Language%20Interpreter%20Rocking%20Out%20at%20Lollapalooza%20Mumbai%20is%20a%20Whole%20Vibe%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%3A%20by%20News18%2C%20Published%20on%201%20February%2C%202023%3C%2Fem%3