20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EUtsow%20Pradhan%20poses%20for%20a%20picture%20outside%20an%20eco-hut%20in%20Tieedi.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nearby%20village%20of%20Rajahatta%2C%20which%20also%20falls%20along%20the%20same%20one-kilometre%20stretch%20of%20road%2C%20has%20a%20similar%20story.%20As%20you%20reach%20the%20stairs%20that%20climb%20up%20a%20forested%20path%2C%20a%20signboard%20introducing%20the%20area%20as%20a%20zero-waste%20village%20greets%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20process%20of%20becoming%20zero-waste%20is%20ongoing%2C%20Utsow%20has%20made%20waste%20collection%20from%20the%20region%20a%20daily%20task%20under%20a%20project%20named%20the%20Green%20Mile%20Project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20task%20might%E2%80%99ve%20been%20herculean%2C%20Ustow%20and%20his%20team%20were%20provided%20the%20necessary%20support%20by%20DCB%20Bank.%20%E2%80%9CDCB%20Bank%20has%20been%20our%20CSR%20partner%20in%20the%20Green%20Mile%20Project%20for%20the%20last%20three%20years.%20They%20played%20an%20instrumental%20role%20in%20funding%20the%20project%20and%20helping%20us%20launch%20the%20three%20zero%20waste%20villages%20of%20Darjeeling%2C%E2%80%9D%20Utsow%20acknowledges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMeet%20the%20waste%20warriors%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20his%20team%2C%20Utsow%20has%20built%20an%20impressive%20waste%20treatment%20facility%20that%20segregates%20waste%20into%2053%20categories%20before%20treating%20or%20recycling%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20walk%20down%20the%20steps%20to%20reach%20the%20building%2C%20Snehal%20Sinalkar%2C%20who%20oversees%20the%20project%20as%20team%20lead%2C%20introduces%20me%20to%20their%20waste%20warriors%20%E2%80%94%20a%20group%20of%20chickens%2C%20two%20rabbits%20expecting%20new%20friends%20soon%2C%20and%20two%20guinea%20pigs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20at%20the%20composting%20pit%2C%20Snehal%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThi