%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture_11zon-1726746932-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture_11zon-1726746932-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366734%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Ambico%20Ice%20Factory%20is%20a%20145-year-old%20heritage%20building%20in%20South%20Bombay%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20did%20this%20transformation%20happen%3F%20An%20%E2%80%9Calmost%20poetic%E2%80%9D%20experience%20that%20Kamal%20Malik%20%E2%80%94%20an%20architect%20with%20almost%20five%20decades%20of%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20had%20when%20his%20eyes%20first%20met%20the%20almost%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F139833%2Fheritage-mumbai-temple-restored%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E150-year-old%20building%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20first%20encounter%20with%20the%20Ice%20Factory%20is%20vividly%20etched%20in%20my%20memory!%20Sunlight%20streaming%20in%20from%20the%20north-light%20Burma%20teak%20trusses%20and%20piercing%20the%20blocks%20of%20ice%20being%20moved%20by%20the%20gantry%20and%20giving%20way%20to%20a%20courtyard%20shaded%20by%20the%20canopy%20of%20a%20huge%20banyan%20tree.%20A%20fertile%20environment%20for%20contemplation%20and%20transformation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAn%20ice%20factory%2C%20a%20banyan%20tree%2C%20and%20the%20birth%20of%20an%20idea%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20set%20sight%20on%20IF.BE%20%E2%80%94%20an%20acronym%20for%20Ice%20Factory%20Bellary%20Estate%20%E2%80%94%20which%20also%20has%20a%20deeper%20meaning%20as%20Malik%20will%20explain%20later%2C%20you%20may%20find%20it%20hard%20to%20believe%20that%20what%20is%20now%20a%20creative%20hub%20for%20the%20arts%2C%20was%20an%20ice%20factory%20a%20century%20ago.%20So%20order%20yourself%20some%3Cem%3E%20matar%20khasta%20%3C%2Fem%3Erolls%20(fried%20finger%20food%20with%20green%20pea%20filling)%20while%20I%20regale%20you%20with%20a%20history%20lesson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIF.BE%E2%80%99s%20walls%2C%20150%20years%20ago%2C%20would%20be%20privy%20to%20conversations%20of%20factory%20workers%20that%20ranged%20from%20whether%20the%20gantry%20was%20working%20properly%20to%20concerns%20about%20being%20able%20to%20meet%20the%20ice%20demand%20of%20fish%20markets%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F72036%2Fmumbai-cafe-military-iconic-widely-loved-why%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESouth%20Bombay%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbico%20Ice%20Factory%20(as%20it%20was%20known%20then)%20enjoyed%20its%20popularity%20for%20decades%20before%20a%20factory%20in%20New%20Bombay%20took%20over%20operations.%20%E2%80%9CIce%20first%20came%20to%20India%20on%20a%20ship%20from%20Boston%20in%20the%201800s%2C%E2%80%9D%20Malik%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-1_11zon-1726747066.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20banyan%20tree%20at%20the%20Ambico%20Ice%20Factory%20caught%20Kamal%20Malik's%20attention%2C%20prompting%20him%20to%20restore%20the%20place%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-1_11zon-1726747066.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-1_11zon-1726747066-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-1_11zon-1726747066-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fup