%20found%20himself%20saying%20a%20%E2%80%98yes%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20project%2C%20joined%20by%20architects%20Amardeep%20Tony%20Singh%20and%20Abhijit%20Mehta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-2-1726747206.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kamal%20Malik%20has%20over%20five%20decades%20of%20experience%20in%20architectural%20projects%20which%20have%20kept%20sustainability%20at%20the%20fore%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-2-1726747206.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-2-1726747206-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-2-1726747206-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-2-1726747206-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-2-1726747206-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366741%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKamal%20Malik%20has%20over%20five%20decades%20of%20experience%20in%20architectural%20projects%20that%20have%20kept%20sustainability%20at%20the%20fore%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELed%20by%20Malik%20Architecture%2C%20the%20team%20embarked%20on%20the%20quest%20to%20give%20the%20ice%20factory%20a%20second%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20IF.BE%20is%20a%2010%2C000-square-foot%20space%20that%20boasts%20five%20sections%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98The%20Banyan%20Tree%20Caf%C3%A9%E2%80%99%3B%20%E2%80%98The%20Substation%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20re