s%20that%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20building%E2%80%99s%20legacy%2C%20in%20a%20more%20nuanced%20fashion.%20Malik%20adds%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332749%2Fex-banker-sunando-sen-built-tanhau-sustainable-himalayan-homestay-corbett-restore-wildlife%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etouches%20of%20sustainability%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20included%20in%20every%20way%20possible.%20For%20months%2C%20the%20team%20scraped%20away%20at%20old%20plaster%2C%20which%20yielded%20brickwork%20and%20vintage%20Burma%20teak%20woodwork%20underneath.%20Look%20around%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20notice%20in%20some%20places%20the%20colours%20don%E2%80%99t%20quite%20match.%20Malik%20underscores%20that%20no%20attempts%20were%20made%20to%20polish%20the%20teak%20wood%20surfaces.%20This%20lends%20a%20rugged%2C%20raw%20touch%20to%20the%20staircase%20at%20the%20Native%20Restaurant%20and%20Bar%2C%20its%20roof%20structure%20and%20flooring%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Ice%20Factory%20roof%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20if%20there%20are%20mismatches%3F%20It%20only%20adds%20to%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20space%2C%20the%20architect%20believes.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20he%20adds%20that%20in%20places%20where%20it%20was%20necessitated%2C%20safety%20upgrades%20were%20made.%20These%20include%20structural%20reinforcements%20to%20the%20walls%20and%20roof.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-3_11zon-1726747460.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IF.BE%20boasts%20five%20sections%20which%20include%20a%20fine-dining%20restaurant%2C%20a%20cafe%2C%20a%20space%20for%20exhibitions%2C%20a%20space%20for%20performances%20and%20a%20reading%20room%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-me