onsibility%20requires%20a%20comprehensive%20approach.%20Public%20health%20systems%2C%20family%20planning%20programmes%2C%20and%20communication%20strategies%20must%20be%20tailored%20to%20promote%20male%20involvement%20actively.%20By%20engaging%20men%20as%20equal%20partners%20in%20family%20planning%2C%20we%20may%20unlock%20a%20critical%20pathway%20to%20driving%20meaningful%20change%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20argues%20Poonam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20sustained%20effort%20in%20behaviour%20change%20communication%2C%20combined%20with%20active%20on-ground%20engagement%20with%20men%2C%20is%20essential%20while%20promoting%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20and%20decision-making%20autonomy.%20The%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20shifting%20mindsets%20and%20addressing%20stereotypes%20to%20empower%20women%20in%20making%20informed%20health%20decisions%2C%20while%20also%20fostering%20open%20communication%20between%20spouses.%20It%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20initiate%20these%20efforts%20early%20by%20engaging%20adolescents%20in%20discussions%20about%20sexual%20and%20reproductive%20health%20and%20rights.%20Additionally%2C%20strategic%20engagement%20is%20needed%20to%20encourage%20men%20to%20consider%20vasectomy%20as%20a%20viable%20family%20planning%20option%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20we%20get%20there%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoonam%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20that%20male%20engagement%20intervention%20needs%20a%20multi-sectoral%20approach.%20Education%2C%20age%20at%20marriage%2C%20health-seeking%20behaviour%2C%20and%20socio-cultural%20norms%20need%20to%20be%20addressed%20simultaneously%20and%20concurrently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20two%20steps%20she%20recommends%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFrontline%20health%20workers%20(ASHAs%2C%20ANMs)%20must%20be%20supported%20and%20male%20health%20workers%20must%20be%20added%20to%20supplement%20the%20existing%20work