ess.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManah%20Wellness%20builds%20%E2%80%9Cemotionally%20healthy%20workplaces%E2%80%9D%20by%20prioritising%20a%20%E2%80%98people-first%E2%80%99%20approach.%20As%20Debasmita%20emphasises%2C%20meaningful%20change%20starts%20from%20the%20top.%20They%20assist%20companies%20in%20creating%20strong%20policies%20that%20focus%20on%20employee%20well-being%2C%20ensuring%20a%20healthier%20and%20more%20supportive%20work%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20normalised%20and%20glorified%20this%20toxic%20culture.%20It%E2%80%99s%20important%20for%20employees%20to%20take%20measures%20for%20their%20own%20well-being%20by%20having%20a%20routine%20and%20focusing%20on%20self-care.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20need%20for%20mentorship%20to%20guide%20youngsters%20on%20how%20to%20handle%20stress%20and%20take%20responsibility%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20can%20companies%20build%20a%20healthy%20workplace%3F%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Col%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHave%20regular%20employee%20pulse%20checks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAsk%20questions%20and%20conduct%20surveys%20or%20focus%20group%20discussions%20to%20understand%20what%20employees%20want.%20This%20can%20help%20in%20forming%20initiatives%20and%20policies%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Debasmita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EConduct%20mental%20health%20screenings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInclude%20mental%20health%20screenings%20just%20like%20the%20physical%20health%20ones%20to%20determine%20who%20needs%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%20people%20across%20the%20organisation%20lead%20the%20initiative%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForm%20committees